-- out/todo.txt --
embedCycle: error in v2 (structural cycle) but success in v3 (close({c}) not truly structural cycle).
closeCycle/structCycle: different error paths reported in v2 vs v3.
disjunctionCycle: different error message format (type list vs list).
forCycle.#A.a: v2 errors directly, v3 shows as ~(forCycle.#B).
listAddCycle/listMulCycle: different error messages between v2 and v3.
letCycleFail.t2: v2 X was a struct, v3 X is structural cycle error.
